result.title: Level 1 Contest
result.content:
The Road to Level 2

To qualify to Level 2, you should pass through two phases:

The Online Qualification Contest

The contest starts this Friday at 6:00 PM and lasts for 24 hours.

You should solve as much problems as you can; this contest will determine whether or not you will qualify to the onsite contest.

It's a 24-hour contest, so there is no excuse not to participate.

The Onsite Contest

The contest will be held in FCIS Ain Shams University.

Details will be announced later.
